graph LR
    RHODSOp[RHODS Operator<br/>rhods-operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    RHODSOp -->|required| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 1.28+<br/>Platform runtime]
    RHODSOp -->|required| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.5<br/>Operator framework]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    RHODSOp -->|conditional<br/>KServe + SSO| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh Operator<br/>Latest]
    RHODSOp -->|conditional<br/>KServe| Serverless[OpenShift Serverless Operator<br/>Latest]
    RHODSOp -->|conditional<br/>KServe authz| Authorino[Authorino Operator<br/>Latest]
    RHODSOp -->|conditional<br/>DSP| Pipelines[OpenShift Pipelines Operator<br/>Latest]
    RHODSOp -.->|optional| PromOp[Prometheus Operator v0.68.0<br/>Monitoring]

    %% Internal ODH Components - Manifest Deployment
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Dashboard[odh-dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Notebooks[odh-notebook-controller<br/>Jupyter notebooks]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KServe[kserve<br/>Model serving]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelMesh[modelmesh-serving<br/>Model serving]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| DSP[data-science-pipelines-operator<br/>ML pipelines]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| CodeFlare[codeflare-operator<br/>Distributed computing]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KubeRay[kuberay-operator<br/>Ray clusters]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Training[training-operator<br/>ML training]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Kueue[kueue<br/>Job queueing]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrustyAI[trustyai-operator<br/>Model explainability]

    %% Component Conflicts
    KServe -.->|incompatible| ModelMesh

    %% External Services
    RHODSOp -->|fetches manifests| GitHub[GitHub<br/>Component repos]
    RHODSOp -->|pulls images| Quay[quay.io<br/>Container images]
    RHODSOp -->|pulls images| RHIO[registry.redhat.io<br/>Red Hat images]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|integrates| K8s
    KServe -->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -->|requires| Serverless
    KServe -->|requires| Authorino
    DSP -->|requires| Pipelines

